) hyaline with yellow brown to dark brown pattern; cell dm with brown band approximately between apical 2 / 5 – 1 / 5 ; wing-thorax ratio 2.6 –3.0, vein R 4 + 5 ratio 1.4–1.5 , vein M ratio 0.31–0.38 , subcosta-costa ratio 0.56–0.67 ; R 4 + 5 dorsally with 10–11 tiny setulae between node and R-M, no setula apical to R-M.
